title: Pix2ASCII
description: Pix2ASCII Art Studio is an AI-powered web app that converts images into high-quality ASCII art. Built with React 19 and Vite 6, and powered by Google Gemini 1.5 Flash, it analyzes images to optimize character palettes, styles, and resolution. With real-time rendering, multiple ASCII styles, color support, and high-resolution exports, it combines retro terminal aesthetics with modern AI performance.
